      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Hikari Comparison\n\n- 기본 sweep: `2026-03-16`, `pool=10/20/30/50/80`\n- 컨텍스트 스위칭 보강: `2026-03-17`, `pool=30/50/80`\n- 상단 링크로 각 run 시간으로 바로 이동하고, 아래 그래프는 선택한 시간 구간을 보여준다.\n- `Host / Process Context Switches` 패널은 `2026-03-17` 보강 구간에서만 값이 나온다.\n\n### Quick Links\n\n- [pool=10](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-15T16:23:13.000Z&to=2026-03-15T16:24:14.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [pool=20](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-15T16:25:03.000Z&to=2026-03-15T16:26:04.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [pool=30](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-15T16:26:52.000Z&to=2026-03-15T16:27:53.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [pool=50](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-15T16:28:42.000Z&to=2026-03-15T16:29:42.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [pool=80](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-15T16:30:31.000Z&to=2026-03-15T16:31:32.000Z&timezone=browser)\n\n### Context Sweep Links\n\n- [context pool=30](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-17T03:33:05.000Z&to=2026-03-17T03:34:06.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [context pool=50](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-17T03:35:03.000Z&to=2026-03-17T03:36:04.000Z&timezone=browser)\n- [context pool=80](http://54.180.143.124:3000/d/hikari-comparison/hikari-comparison?from=2026-03-17T03:37:01.000Z&to=2026-03-17T03:38:01.000Z&timezone=browser)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Summary Table",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
