      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "| pool | RPS | avg | p95 | pending max | threads_connected max | notes |\n| ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- |\n| `10` | `82.52/s` | `101.22ms` | `271.35ms` | `16` | `11` | 부족 |\n| `20` | `89.46/s` | `55.37ms` | `152.22ms` | `3` | `22` | 개선 |\n| `30` | `93.22/s` | `33.11ms` | `84.03ms` | `3` | `22` | knee point |\n| `50` | `92.88/s` | `33.10ms` | `89.17ms` | `1` | `21` | 이득 작음 |\n| `80` | `93.58/s` | `31.21ms` | `74.59ms` | `0` | `22` | 미세 개선 |\n\n### Context Sweep (`2026-03-17`)\n\n| pool | RPS | avg | p95 | host ctxt/s max | mysql voluntary | mysql nonvoluntary |\n| ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| `30` | `58.61/s` | `348.62ms` | `823.47ms` | `29218.65` | `4081.75` | `1132.97` |\n| `50` | `65.28/s` | `262.03ms` | `545.10ms` | `29044.17` | `4053.87` | `1374.85` |\n| `80` | `74.77/s` | `162.59ms` | `354.71ms` | `29942.91` | `4206.13` | `1520.73` |"
      }
    },
